    {
        "text": "...by comparing a society to a ship.",
        "startTime": 19567,
        "endTime": 21993,
        "slowStartTime": 29500,
        "slowEndTime": 33215
    },
    {
        "text": "\"If you were heading out on a journey by sea,\" asked Socrates,...",
        "startTime": 22363,
        "endTime": 25332,
        "slowStartTime": 33695,
        "slowEndTime": 38223
    },
    {
