        "startTime": 33997,
        "endTime": 36269,
        "slowStartTime": 51145,
        "slowEndTime": 54628
    },
    {
        "text": "\"So why then,\" responds Socrates, \"do we keep thinking...",
        "startTime": 36601,
        "endTime": 39091,
        "slowStartTime": 55052,
        "slowEndTime": 58862
    },
    {
        "text": "...that any old person should be fit to judge...",
        "startTime": 39175,
        "endTime": 41409,
        "slowStartTime": 58913,
        "slowEndTime": 62339
    },
    {
        "text": "...who should be the ruler of a country?\"",
        "startTime": 41650,
        "endTime": 43487,
        "slowStartTime": 62625,
        "slowEndTime": 65456
    },
    {
        "text": "Socrates' point is that voting in an election is a skill...",
        "startTime": 44103,
        "endTime": 47521,
        "slowStartTime": 66304,
        "slowEndTime": 71506
    },
    {
        "text": "...not a random intuition,...",
        "startTime": 47827,
        "endTime": 49345,
        "slowStartTime": 71891,
        "slowEndTime": 74243
